'''四柱清真寺'''（{{lang-ar|أربع روكون}}）是[[索馬里|索馬里]]首都[[摩加迪沙|摩加迪沙]]的一座[[清真寺|清真寺]]。

清真寺建於[[伊斯蘭曆|伊斯蘭曆]]667年，即公元1268-69年間，與[[法赫魯·丁清真寺|法赫魯·丁清真寺]]同是市內最古老的清真寺之一。寺內的[[米哈拉布|米哈拉布]]刻有銘文，說明了清真寺建成日期，並紀念清真寺的創建人、庫舒拉‧伊本‧穆巴拉克‧設拉子（又名庫舒拉‧伊本‧穆罕默德）。<ref name="Aaarpvst">{{cite book|title=AARP, Art and Archaeology Research Papers, Volumes 7-12|year=1975|page=8|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=IXVXAAAAMAAJ|access-date=2015-07-27|archive-date=2016-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603122723/https://books.google.com/books?id=IXVXAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Garlake">{{cite book|last=Garlake|first=Peter S.|title=The Early Islamic Architecture of the East African Coast|year=1966|publisher=Institute|page=10|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=IRINAQAAIAAJ|access-date=2015-07-27|archive-date=2014-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626224130/http://books.google.com/books?id=IRINAQAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>
